oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Old South Jamboree Job No. 21600
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Typed invoice for an order placed by Glen Hodges of the Old South Jamboree for 100 two color window cards announcing at the Old South Jamboree Jimmy C. Newman on January 10, Shoji Tabuchi and Peggy Forman on January 17, and Bill Anderson on January 24. Receipt indicates agreed price, size, order quantity, shipping location and description.
